  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK368">
<l>avāvillārk killākun tuṉpamaḵ tuṇṭēṟ</l>
<l>ṟavāatu mēṉmēl varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no sorrow to those who are without desire; but where that is, (sorrow) will incessantly come, more and more.</l>
            </lg>
